description: Demolition of existing building and structures with the exception of the facades of numbers 2 to 8 and 16 to 32 (even) De Vere Gardens (including the Victoria Road frontage) and development of new building incorporating retained facades to provide 97 residential units, ancillary basement parking, highway works, new vehicular and pedestrian accesses, ancillary basement health and fitness facility, all necessary enabling works and associated hard and soft landscaping.
